          <h4>120 &euro; / person</h4>
            Fish, Fillet-O-Fish <br>
            Wraps, Grilled Chicken Foldover <br>
            Vegetarian, Veggie Burger <br>
            Salads, Crispy Chicken Salad Green Salad <br>
            Sides, Corn Cup, McFries
          </div>
        </div>
        <div id="tab-body-3" class="chef-menu-tab-body hidden">
